text: @UPS @UPSHelp I was supposed to get a call back from my local center about a misdelivered package. No call received. How can I get in contact with them or the driver?
@iansvo I'll be happy to help you with this delivery. Please DM your tracking number, complete address and contact information. ^KS https://t.co/wKJHDXWGRQ

I've now been promised a call by @UPS 2 times, and have yet to receive any class. 

My package wasn't delivered because no one was present, yet this wasn't made known in advance at any point, so I didn't know someone had to be there. 

Overall rather awful customer experience.
